tent="Cách viết khác">&#160256;</span></a><a href="/whv/𧨈"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#162312;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩁻"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168059;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩂊"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168074;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩂳"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168115;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩃏"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168143;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩃗"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168151;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩃞"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168158;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩄇"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168199;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩅶"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168310;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩆒"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168338;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩆕"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168341;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩆜"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168348;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩆮"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168366;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩇎"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#168398;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Chữ gần giống <span class="badge">4</span></p>
				<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/靈"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#xF9B3;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩆕"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x29195;</span></a><a href="/whv/𠠢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x20822;</span></a><a href="/whv/孁"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5B41;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
